title: Bug 132103 - No objects under Context in palette when scripting a data set
OB: When scripting a data set, there are no objects displayed under the Context section in the palette.
EB: The expected behavior is to have objects listed under the Context section in the palette when scripting a data set.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the application.
2. Navigate to the data set scripting section.
3. Attempt to view the objects listed under the Context section in the palette.
